  39:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** /* File Info : -----------------------------------------------------------------
  40:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****                                    User NOTES
  41:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** 1. How To use this driver:
  42:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** --------------------------
  43:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****    - This driver is used to drive directly an LCD TFT using LTDC controller.
  44:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****    - This driver select dynamically the mounted LCD, ILI9341 240x320 LCD mounted 
  45:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      on MB1075B discovery board, and use the adequate timing and setting for 
  46:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** 	 the specified LCD using device ID of the ILI9341 mounted on MB1075B discovery board           
  47:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** 
  48:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** 2. Driver description:
  49:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** ---------------------
  50:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   + Initialization steps :
  51:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      o Initialize the LCD using the LCD_Init() function.
  52:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      o Apply the Layer configuration using LCD_LayerDefaultInit() function    
  53:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      o Select the LCD layer to be used using LCD_SelectLayer() function.
  54:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      o Enable the LCD display using LCD_DisplayOn() function.
  55:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** 
  56:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   + Options
  57:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      o Configure and enable the color keying functionality using LCD_SetColorKeying()
  58:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****        function.
  59:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****      o Modify in the fly the transparency and/or the frame buffer address
  60:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****        using the following functions :
  61:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****        - LCD_SetTransparency()
  62:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****        - LCD_SetLayerAddress() 
  63:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   
  64:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   + Display on LCD
  65:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****       o Clear the hole LCD using LCD_Clear() function or only one specified string
  66:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****         line using LCD_ClearStringLine() function.
  67:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****       o Display a character on the specified line and column using LCD_DisplayChar()
  68:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****         function or a complete string line using LCD_DisplayStringAtLine() function.
  69:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****       o Display a string line on the specified position (x,y in pixel) and align mode
  70:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****         using LCD_DisplayStringAtLine() function.          
  71:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****       o Draw and fill a basic shapes (dot, line, rectangle, circle, ellipse, .. bitmap) 
  72:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****         on LCD using the available set of functions     
  73:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****  
  74:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** ------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
