 152:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c **** /**
 153:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   * @brief  Initializes the LCD.
 154:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   * @param  None
 155:Drivers/BSP/STM32F429I-Discovery/stm32f429i_discovery_lcd.c ****   * @retval LCD state
